    <h3>District Information</h3>
    <p>Serving 73,000 students, the Brevard School District is the 10 th largest district in Florida
and has listed as an "A" rated school within the state. Working with high quality teachers,
and keeping up a challenging, yet effective, curriculum, this district is helping to deliver
excellence to its students every day. With a variety of different athletic programs and music
programs, students are allowed to excel where ever they feel best fits them. In fact, in 2009
the county was designated by the state as a "Music Demonstration School", which is a pride
for many of the people in the community. With a mission to enhance every student's life
and a vision to deliver a culture of dedication, collaboration and learning, Brevard Public
Schools are certainly leading the way to success in the future!</p>
